1
00:00:01,280 --> 00:00:04,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tonari's battle against 
the Nokkers continues.</i></font>

2
00:00:04,770 --> 00:00:05,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fushi!</font>

3
00:00:05,700 --> 00:00:07,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do something! Please!</font>

4
00:00:07,190 --> 00:00:08,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fushi!</font>

5
00:00:10,290 --> 00:00:15,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In the moment of certain doom, 
Fushi's friends come to her aid.</i></font>

6
00:00:19,870 --> 00:00:21,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I made it.</font>

7
00:00:21,860 --> 00:00:27,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Meanwhile, Yuki's team rescues 
Mizuha from the underground.</i></font>

8
00:02:00,010 --> 00:02:04,010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="30" color="#291907">Clean Water</font>

9
00:02:04,970 --> 00:02:07,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can trust you, right?</font>

10
00:02:07,650 --> 00:02:09,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of you?</font>

11
00:02:20,610 --> 00:02:22,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you please drink this?</font>

12
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:26,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a pact ritual that's been 
passed down by the Guardians.</font>

13
00:02:26,700 --> 00:02:31,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those who become one of us, of our 
friends, of our family, all drink this.</font>

14
00:02:31,740 --> 00:02:35,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It proves that we will always trust each 
other and would never betray one another.</font>

15
00:02:38,490 --> 00:02:39,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry.</font>

16
00:02:39,780 --> 00:02:41,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just water.</font>

17
00:02:42,790 --> 00:02:44,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if we drink it...</font>

18
00:02:45,530 --> 00:02:47,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you'll come with us?</font>

19
00:02:48,430 --> 00:02:49,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

20
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:52,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are we sure about this water?</font>

21
00:02:56,460 --> 00:02:57,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can do it, right?</font>

22
00:03:05,450 --> 00:03:06,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't do it!</font>

23
00:03:18,620 --> 00:03:20,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, let's go.</font>

24
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:25,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All you guys over there are 
coming to my place, too.</font>

25
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:27,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bon-san, could you contact Gramps</font>

26
00:03:27,630 --> 00:03:30,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and let him know I'm bringing 
a ton of people over?</font>

27
00:03:30,220 --> 00:03:32,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My phone's busted.</font>

28
00:03:33,810 --> 00:03:35,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait.</font>

29
00:03:35,980 --> 00:03:38,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're interesting, Yuki-kun.</font>

30
00:03:38,140 --> 00:03:40,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You get hurt a lot, don't you?</font>

31
00:03:40,290 --> 00:03:43,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem like the type to 
not think things through.</font>

32
00:03:43,340 --> 00:03:45,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if it's a trap?</font>

33
00:03:45,340 --> 00:03:47,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If the water is poisoned?</font>

34
00:03:47,970 --> 00:03:51,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Yuki sure is a man of reckless courage.</font>

35
00:03:51,450 --> 00:03:53,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You aren't one to talk, are you?</font>

36
00:03:53,350 --> 00:03:55,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, is it poisoned?</font>

37
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:57,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course not.</font>

38
00:03:57,230 --> 00:03:59,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's my dear underclassman at school.</font>

39
00:03:59,490 --> 00:04:01,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It really is just water.</font>

40
00:04:02,630 --> 00:04:06,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I asked if you and I, human and mutant,</font>

41
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:09,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">could be friends, you said yes.</font>

42
00:04:09,070 --> 00:04:12,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did we say that?</font>

43
00:04:14,890 --> 00:04:19,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe what people say, 
no matter what they are.</font>

44
00:04:19,570 --> 00:04:21,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter <i>what</i> I am?</font>

45
00:04:21,960 --> 00:04:23,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Mizuha.</font>

46
00:04:23,830 --> 00:04:26,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all back to normal!</font>

47
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:30,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Nokkers are gone, 
and the water was safe to drink!</font>

48
00:04:30,460 --> 00:04:32,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Nokker's still here.</font>

49
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:35,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I've been talking to it this whole time.</font>

50
00:04:36,770 --> 00:04:39,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? So you mean...</font>

51
00:04:39,020 --> 00:04:43,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's still lurking in our midst?</font>

52
00:04:43,010 --> 00:04:46,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what's your name?</font>

53
00:04:46,820 --> 00:04:51,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? I-I told you, I'm Mizuha.</font>

54
00:04:54,410 --> 00:04:57,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuha-senpai is right-handed.</font>

55
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:17,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's gone.</font>

56
00:05:19,170 --> 00:05:20,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aoki-kun!</font>

57
00:05:20,500 --> 00:05:21,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vice President!</font>

58
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:23,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get a grip!</font>

59
00:05:23,910 --> 00:05:25,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go see Satoru.</font>

60
00:05:26,340 --> 00:05:28,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry about me.</font>

61
00:05:29,420 --> 00:05:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We gotta go shopping for everyone's dinner.</font>

62
00:05:33,380 --> 00:05:38,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fushi will bring Mizuha-senpai's 
Nokker to us.</font>

63
00:05:38,950 --> 00:05:42,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we can talk it over,</font>

64
00:05:42,030 --> 00:05:46,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and they'll return Mizuha-senpai's 
body along with all the others.</font>

65
00:05:46,780 --> 00:05:49,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can come to an understanding.</font>

66
00:05:49,270 --> 00:05:50,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have faith that we can.</font>

67
00:05:51,210 --> 00:05:53,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sheesh, you...</font>

68
00:05:53,540 --> 00:05:55,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How happy-go-lucky can you be?</font>

69
00:05:56,030 --> 00:05:59,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder how Mizuha-kun would 
have reacted if she were here.</font>

70
00:05:59,660 --> 00:06:03,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd be happy just to see her 
cringing at me like always.</font>

71
00:06:28,220 --> 00:06:30,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right, Fushi-sama?</font>

72
00:06:30,700 --> 00:06:34,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, Chamihiko-san, 
but could you take care of Grandpa?</font>

73
00:06:34,100 --> 00:06:36,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, but why...</font>

74
00:06:36,200 --> 00:06:37,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's coming.</font>

75
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:40,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fushi-sama!</font>

76
00:06:48,330 --> 00:06:50,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Fushi.</font>

77
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:53,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. What's up?</font>

78
00:06:53,350 --> 00:06:58,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've always wanted to fight 
you properly sometime.</font>

79
00:06:58,520 --> 00:07:01,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which of us is stronger?</font>

80
00:07:05,010 --> 00:07:08,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm pretty sure you'll 
end up back in Paradise.</font>

81
00:07:26,170 --> 00:07:29,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you giving up on your ambitions?</font>

82
00:07:37,290 --> 00:07:41,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll reconsider if you defeat me.</font>

83
00:07:55,980 --> 00:07:58,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this supposed to stop me?</font>

84
00:07:58,380 --> 00:07:59,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're too slow!</font>

85
00:08:22,090 --> 00:08:23,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

86
00:08:23,260 --> 00:08:25,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why? Why? Why?</font>

87
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:27,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why? Why?</font>

88
00:08:27,730 --> 00:08:29,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?!</font>

89
00:08:40,380 --> 00:08:42,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you going easy on me?</font>

90
00:08:42,610 --> 00:08:46,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you see that I'm taking this seriously?</font>

91
00:08:52,730 --> 00:08:56,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were you influenced by that 
friend of yours, Yuki?</font>

92
00:08:56,350 --> 00:08:58,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like that boy.</font>

93
00:09:02,550 --> 00:09:06,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He didn't hesitate to drink 
the water with Nokkers in it.</font>

94
00:09:06,470 --> 00:09:08,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As a sign of friendship.</font>

95
00:09:09,090 --> 00:09:10,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuki did?!</font>

96
00:09:14,270 --> 00:09:17,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't tell me this is all you've got!</font>

97
00:09:34,090 --> 00:09:36,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This ought to be enough space.</font>

98
00:09:37,750 --> 00:09:40,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on and take your weapon.</font>

99
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:42,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your bow.</font>

100
00:09:42,500 --> 00:09:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your sword.</font>

101
00:09:43,680 --> 00:09:44,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

102
00:09:44,730 --> 00:09:46,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuki rubbed off on me.</font>

103
00:09:47,130 --> 00:09:50,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to kill you.</font>

104
00:09:50,130 --> 00:09:54,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm hoping that we can come to understand 
each other while we're both alive.</font>

105
00:10:05,660 --> 00:10:06,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

106
00:10:14,180 --> 00:10:17,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It isn't over yet, Fushi.</font>

107
00:10:27,820 --> 00:10:29,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You moved your core.</font>

108
00:10:29,820 --> 00:10:33,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think you can defeat me in that body?</font>

109
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:35,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you really willing to do this?</font>

110
00:10:35,890 --> 00:10:37,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about you?</font>

111
00:10:37,090 --> 00:10:40,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you cold in that 
clothing made of skin?</font>

112
00:10:53,090 --> 00:10:55,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall we continue, Fushi?</font>

113
00:10:56,210 --> 00:11:00,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you want to find out how 
meaningless your platitudes are?</font>

114
00:11:00,340 --> 00:11:02,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you really want to go on?</font>

115
00:11:02,970 --> 00:11:08,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You think my offer to debate you 
instead of killing you is a platitude?</font>

116
00:11:08,410 --> 00:11:11,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you expect? It's only human.</font>

117
00:11:11,180 --> 00:11:14,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But neither of us is human.</font>

118
00:11:16,770 --> 00:11:19,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">God damn it, Chami.</font>

119
00:11:19,610 --> 00:11:22,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's still more ammo in the storage.</font>

120
00:11:22,820 --> 00:11:23,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heya.</font>

121
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:25,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want some help, Mizuha?</font>

122
00:11:25,950 --> 00:11:28,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, Daddy.</font>

123
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:30,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He isn't using his true strength yet.</font>

124
00:11:30,410 --> 00:11:32,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cut him some slack.</font>

125
00:11:32,900 --> 00:11:37,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've already taken the best 
of the Great Fushi's vessels.</font>

126
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:40,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's only got the feeble ones left.</font>

127
00:11:40,290 --> 00:11:42,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, wanna use this, Fushi-sama?</font>

128
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:45,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, thanks.</font>

129
00:11:45,340 --> 00:11:48,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Entertain her properly, then, would you?</font>

130
00:11:48,170 --> 00:11:50,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You still have some that 
you can use, don't you?</font>

131
00:11:52,590 --> 00:11:54,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been hiding some?</font>

132
00:11:57,100 --> 00:11:58,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Show them!</font>

133
00:12:05,800 --> 00:12:07,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't hiding any.</font>

134
00:12:07,990 --> 00:12:10,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just waiting for the 
right reason to face you.</font>

135
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:13,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sixth descendant...</font>

136
00:12:13,950 --> 00:12:15,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kahaku!</font>

137
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:21,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The failure of a vessel!</font>

138
00:12:27,660 --> 00:12:29,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't insult my friends.</font>

139
00:12:29,940 --> 00:12:31,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come get some more!</font>

140
00:12:31,980 --> 00:12:33,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me set you straight.</font>

141
00:12:33,090 --> 00:12:34,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Draw your weapon, Fushi!</font>

142
00:12:36,370 --> 00:12:38,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's making you strong...</font>

143
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:46,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is the blood of your ancestors 
coursing through your body.</font>

144
00:12:51,970 --> 00:12:53,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It hurts!</font>

145
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:57,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems you aren't accustomed to pain yet.</font>

146
00:12:58,140 --> 00:13:01,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I doubt you're ready for death, 
judging from your reaction.</font>

147
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:16,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you mental?</font>

148
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:18,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you trying to accomplish?</font>

149
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you need a place to go,</font>

150
00:13:21,590 --> 00:13:24,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be your vessel.</font>

151
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:28,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure?</font>

152
00:13:28,270 --> 00:13:31,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd take all your vessels from you.</font>

153
00:13:31,910 --> 00:13:37,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know how well I can keep 
the contaminant that is you at bay.</font>

154
00:13:37,060 --> 00:13:41,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if it turns out that 
you're stronger, well...</font>

155
00:13:41,650 --> 00:13:43,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll cross that bridge when I get to it.</font>

156
00:13:43,270 --> 00:13:45,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have a plan?!</font>

157
00:13:58,140 --> 00:14:00,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Why?!</font>

158
00:14:00,970 --> 00:14:02,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Relax.</font>

159
00:14:02,310 --> 00:14:04,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I let the main body evaporate.</font>

160
00:14:04,920 --> 00:14:06,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I mean....</font>

161
00:14:07,060 --> 00:14:10,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I figured it's time we head home, too.</font>

162
00:14:10,650 --> 00:14:14,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Try as we might to kill you, 
we couldn't find your core.</font>

163
00:14:14,110 --> 00:14:17,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we were no match for your birth parent.</font>

164
00:14:17,370 --> 00:14:20,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our battle in the current age is over.</font>

165
00:14:20,710 --> 00:14:22,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the <i>current</i> age?</font>

166
00:14:22,650 --> 00:14:24,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We aren't done yet.</font>

167
00:14:24,560 --> 00:14:26,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're in the middle of living, too.</font>

168
00:14:27,230 --> 00:14:29,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That one came here to be killed.</font>

169
00:14:30,460 --> 00:14:31,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To start over.</font>

170
00:14:33,020 --> 00:14:35,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The water here is contaminated with Nokkers.</font>

171
00:14:35,760 --> 00:14:37,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wash them away.</font>

172
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:41,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take them to the sea, and they'll decide 
for themselves whether to live or die.</font>

173
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:49,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't get the wrong idea.</font>

174
00:14:49,030 --> 00:14:51,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You haven't won.</font>

175
00:14:52,160 --> 00:14:55,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're lucky I'm here, huh, Fushi?</font>

176
00:14:58,350 --> 00:14:59,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Later.</font>

177
00:15:04,670 --> 00:15:08,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Fushi!</font>

178
00:15:08,170 --> 00:15:10,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You around?</font>

179
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:12,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are you?</font>

180
00:15:12,090 --> 00:15:14,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right?</font>

181
00:15:14,890 --> 00:15:17,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See? It's a total maze down here.</font>

182
00:15:17,060 --> 00:15:19,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe Fushi-san's 
group found their way.</font>

183
00:15:19,860 --> 00:15:21,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed.</font>

184
00:15:21,060 --> 00:15:22,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say, what about us?</font>

185
00:15:22,310 --> 00:15:24,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are we right now?</font>

186
00:15:32,980 --> 00:15:34,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Water.</font>

187
00:15:37,950 --> 00:15:40,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't tell me you're lost, Prince.</font>

188
00:15:40,970 --> 00:15:41,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eh?</font>

189
00:15:41,850 --> 00:15:45,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you two were leading the way.</font>

190
00:15:45,140 --> 00:15:46,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We weren't.</font>

191
00:15:46,700 --> 00:15:49,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't we tell you that 
we don't remember the way?</font>

192
00:15:49,640 --> 00:15:52,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yipes! What if we're trapped?!</font>

193
00:15:52,480 --> 00:15:54,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't bring food or water!</font>

194
00:15:54,480 --> 00:15:56,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay calm, please.</font>

195
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:57,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll bring some.</font>

196
00:15:57,860 --> 00:15:59,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? Thankies!</font>

197
00:15:59,460 --> 00:16:01,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, no!</font>

198
00:16:01,060 --> 00:16:03,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y'all are ghosts!</font>

199
00:16:12,280 --> 00:16:14,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That solves that problem, Prince!</font>

200
00:16:14,060 --> 00:16:14,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have water!</font>

201
00:16:14,940 --> 00:16:16,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is too much!</font>

202
00:16:19,350 --> 00:16:20,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice, it's the exit.</font>

203
00:16:20,870 --> 00:16:22,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the entrance!</font>

204
00:16:27,890 --> 00:16:29,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were looking for Fushi!</font>

205
00:16:29,700 --> 00:16:31,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're all the way back outside!</font>

206
00:16:32,510 --> 00:16:33,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bon.</font>

207
00:16:35,240 --> 00:16:36,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fushi!</font>

208
00:16:36,500 --> 00:16:38,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank goodness you're safe!</font>

209
00:16:39,370 --> 00:16:41,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well? Did you settle things?</font>

210
00:16:41,990 --> 00:16:43,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Settle things?</font>

211
00:16:45,070 --> 00:16:46,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

212
00:16:47,320 --> 00:16:50,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It didn't work out.</font>

213
00:16:51,560 --> 00:16:55,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We couldn't start anything over.</font>

214
00:17:06,030 --> 00:17:08,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spares that you kept for insurance?</font>

215
00:17:08,720 --> 00:17:09,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

216
00:17:09,830 --> 00:17:11,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never used them.</font>

217
00:17:11,120 --> 00:17:13,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's absolutely fantastic.</font>

218
00:17:13,940 --> 00:17:17,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, we should head back to school.</font>

219
00:17:17,190 --> 00:17:18,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">School?</font>

220
00:17:19,100 --> 00:17:21,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bon, I'm going to head there first.</font>

221
00:17:26,190 --> 00:17:27,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fu-chan!</font>

222
00:17:28,120 --> 00:17:29,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fushi-kun.</font>

223
00:17:29,150 --> 00:17:30,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guys!</font>

224
00:17:30,670 --> 00:17:33,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hey... um...</font>

225
00:17:33,610 --> 00:17:37,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just as you wanted, 
I captured the Nokkers alive.</font>

226
00:17:38,370 --> 00:17:42,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll send them out to sea later 
and let them decide where to go.</font>

227
00:17:43,390 --> 00:17:44,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about Tonari?</font>

228
00:17:44,910 --> 00:17:46,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tonari's dead.</font>

229
00:17:46,170 --> 00:17:47,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I killed her good.</font>

230
00:17:47,780 --> 00:17:48,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

231
00:17:51,570 --> 00:17:53,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at your face!</font>

232
00:17:53,790 --> 00:17:56,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't freak out just because I'm dead.</font>

233
00:17:56,850 --> 00:17:58,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">T-T...</font>

234
00:18:00,170 --> 00:18:01,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">T-Tonari!</font>

235
00:18:01,680 --> 00:18:03,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shocked, huh?</font>

236
00:18:03,780 --> 00:18:07,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That kid, Satoru, was it? 
He brought me back to life.</font>

237
00:18:07,150 --> 00:18:09,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up with him? 
Do you know him, Fushi?</font>

238
00:18:09,960 --> 00:18:12,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. It must have hurt.</font>

239
00:18:12,940 --> 00:18:14,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my fault.</font>

240
00:18:14,980 --> 00:18:18,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stupid! Don't apologize for that!</font>

241
00:18:18,890 --> 00:18:20,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never mind that.</font>

242
00:18:21,320 --> 00:18:23,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should have told us!</font>

243
00:18:23,390 --> 00:18:27,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've been friends for centuries, you know?</font>

244
00:18:27,410 --> 00:18:29,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You ought to rely on us.</font>

245
00:18:29,040 --> 00:18:30,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No kidding.</font>

246
00:18:30,430 --> 00:18:32,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're getting an earful later.</font>

247
00:18:54,750 --> 00:18:56,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tanasen!</font>

248
00:18:58,860 --> 00:18:59,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

249
00:18:59,970 --> 00:19:02,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank goodness she isn't dead!</font>

250
00:19:05,290 --> 00:19:06,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this?!</font>

251
00:19:06,820 --> 00:19:08,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened here?!</font>

252
00:19:08,930 --> 00:19:10,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We did it.</font>

253
00:19:10,700 --> 00:19:11,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tee-hee.</font>

254
00:19:11,800 --> 00:19:14,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were fighting off a baddie.</font>

255
00:19:20,250 --> 00:19:21,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Odd...</font>

256
00:19:21,450 --> 00:19:23,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not a single soul in sight.</font>

257
00:19:23,470 --> 00:19:25,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one's coming home.</font>

258
00:19:25,740 --> 00:19:27,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on?</font>

259
00:19:30,210 --> 00:19:32,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The bear's gone, too.</font>

260
00:19:32,290 --> 00:19:34,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never would have thought 
the day would come.</font>

261
00:19:34,990 --> 00:19:38,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many cups of rice am 
I supposed to cook tonight?</font>

262
00:19:43,200 --> 00:19:44,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gramps!</font>

263
00:19:44,680 --> 00:19:46,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm home!</font>

264
00:19:46,210 --> 00:19:47,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuki.</font>

265
00:19:49,090 --> 00:19:51,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I brought a ton of guests over.</font>

266
00:19:51,410 --> 00:19:53,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make, like, a hundred cups of rice!</font>

267
00:19:53,560 --> 00:19:56,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Who's that behind you?</font>

268
00:19:56,250 --> 00:19:59,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't Bon-san message you?</font>

269
00:20:01,370 --> 00:20:03,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grandpa! Onii-chan!</font>

270
00:20:03,420 --> 00:20:04,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aiko!</font>

271
00:20:04,840 --> 00:20:07,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad you're safe.</font>

272
00:20:11,180 --> 00:20:13,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong? What happened?</font>

273
00:20:14,260 --> 00:20:15,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll explain.</font>

274
00:20:16,250 --> 00:20:19,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But first, let's have dinner.</font>

275
00:20:23,990 --> 00:20:26,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then there was this flame, like, bam!</font>

276
00:20:26,870 --> 00:20:29,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wouldn't believe how bad it was.</font>

277
00:20:30,250 --> 00:20:32,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was insane.</font>

278
00:20:32,330 --> 00:20:35,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, I'm impressed you kids 
pulled that off on your own.</font>

279
00:20:35,950 --> 00:20:37,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only because Tonari-san was there.</font>

280
00:20:38,340 --> 00:20:41,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah, it was mostly Aiko.</font>

281
00:20:41,350 --> 00:20:44,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her ideas and quick thinking saved us.</font>

282
00:20:44,380 --> 00:20:46,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it wasn't that big a deal.</font>

283
00:20:46,600 --> 00:20:50,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't have done anything 
without the rest of you.</font>

284
00:20:50,390 --> 00:20:52,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here, Satoru-kun.</font>

285
00:20:52,920 --> 00:20:56,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So he's the Black One that 
Fushi-san was talking about?</font>

286
00:20:57,080 --> 00:20:58,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup.</font>

287
00:20:58,480 --> 00:21:00,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's hard to believe...</font>

288
00:21:00,870 --> 00:21:04,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but after seeing him capture the Nokkers...</font>

289
00:21:05,920 --> 00:21:08,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Salt works on the Nokkers?!</font>

290
00:21:08,450 --> 00:21:09,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

291
00:21:09,320 --> 00:21:12,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've confirmed that holy salt is effective.</font>

292
00:21:12,070 --> 00:21:14,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although it only really 
slowed it down a little.</font>

293
00:21:14,270 --> 00:21:16,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See? I knew we should have used it!</font>

294
00:21:16,930 --> 00:21:19,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My bad. We'll do that next time.</font>

295
00:21:19,450 --> 00:21:22,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time?! No way, no more!</font>

296
00:21:22,340 --> 00:21:24,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}But we were so badass.</font>

297
00:21:22,620 --> 00:21:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I kinda like this.</font>

298
00:21:24,470 --> 00:21:26,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I don't care!</font>

299
00:21:24,920 --> 00:21:27,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's like real teamwork.</font>

300
00:21:27,930 --> 00:21:31,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Did I say something weird?</font>

301
00:21:31,100 --> 00:21:34,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's not a teamwork thing.</font>

302
00:21:34,630 --> 00:21:37,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, we were at each other's throats.</font>

303
00:21:37,010 --> 00:21:39,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We aren't friends at all.</font>

304
00:21:39,280 --> 00:21:41,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, c'mon.</font>

305
00:21:41,660 --> 00:21:44,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, what were you up to, Hanna-san?</font>

306
00:21:44,590 --> 00:21:47,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard you were off somewhere with Yuki-kun.</font>

307
00:21:47,310 --> 00:21:49,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, um, well...</font>

308
00:21:49,640 --> 00:21:51,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

309
00:21:51,100 --> 00:21:54,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was, um...</font>

310
00:21:54,330 --> 00:21:58,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I went to bring Mizuha back.</font>

311
00:22:01,360 --> 00:22:04,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We couldn't bring her back.</font>

312
00:22:05,880 --> 00:22:10,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, everyone, eat well.</font>

313
00:22:22,240 --> 00:22:23,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come with me.</font>

314
00:22:37,700 --> 00:22:41,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuha-senpai! We were waiting for you!</font>

315
00:22:41,420 --> 00:22:42,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome back!</font>

316
00:22:42,510 --> 00:22:43,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome home.</font>

317
00:22:43,630 --> 00:22:44,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

318
00:22:47,700 --> 00:22:50,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did well.</font>

319
00:24:29,980 --> 00:24:55,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="20">{\an8}Preview</font>

320
00:24:32,020 --> 00:24:37,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In an effort to live alongside the Nokkers,</i></font>

321
00:24:37,520 --> 00:24:41,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yuki engages in talks with a certain person.</i></font>

322
00:24:43,130 --> 00:24:49,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>At a loss for direction, Fushi 
grows increasingly frustrated.</i></font>

323
00:24:49,330 --> 00:24:52,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Will he accept yet another power?</i></font>

324
00:24:52,010 --> 00:24:55,010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="30" color="#291907">Coexist</font>

